Version 0.3.15

Bitcointalk

2010-11-13 23:26:40 UTC - [11]Original Post

   Version 0.3.15 is now available.
   Changes:
   - paytxfee switch is now per KB, so it adds the correct fee for large
   transactions
   - sending avoids using coins with less than 6 confirmations if it can
   - BitcoinMiner processes transactions in priority order based on age of
   dependencies
   - make sure generation doesnʼt start before block 74000 downloaded
   - bugfixes by Dean Gores
   - testnet, keypoololdest and paytxfee added to getinfo
